parameters: \F[nakosu_trouble]\FF[iruka_trouble]\AA[2]Iruka: "Are we back to normal? The world... and us?"

\F[ajiri_trouble2]\FF[iruka_trouble]\AA[1]Yui: "What... what does this mean...!? Freedom Poison is...
Agent Sirius turned into a human by themselves!?"

\F[ajiri_trouble2]\FF[ayaka_smile]\AA[2]Ayaka: "The monster... Akane-san was defeated? If the
original Poison is gone, does everything go back to
normal...?"

\F[yurisu_trouble]\FF[ayaka_smile]\AA[1]Yurika: "I don't understand. Poison Burst didn't work... so
why?"

\F[beni_nadeshy]Akane: "I-I guess I just fell too much in love with
Nadeshiko, and even without freedom... it became okay..."

\F[beni_nadeshy]\FF[nakosu_trouble]\AA[1]Akane: "Ugh... don't look at me with those eyes...
Nadeshiko"

\F[beni_nadeshy]\FF[nakosu_trouble]\AA[1]Akane: "It's not that I want to become Nadeshiko or
anything... it's just... my feelings took shape, sort of."

\F[beni_nadeshy]\FF[yurisu_trouble]\AA[2]Yurika: "So, you're saying your kink changed and that
changed the monster's form too! Akane...! To think you feel
that strongly about Nadeshiko..."

\F[beni_nadeshy]\FF[himawari_smile]\AA[2]Himawari: "A kink for loving Nadeshiko? It's a bit off-
putting but also kind of enviable...?"

\F[beni_nadeshy]\FF[himawari_smile]\AA[1]Akane: "That's why! Nadeshiko is here, so be a little more
gentle..."

\F[beni_nadeshy]\FF[sumire_smile]\AA[2]Sumire: "To think such a thing could happen... Being
confessed to... confirming love for each other, and the
hidden feelings overflowing..."

\F[beni_nadeshy]\FF[kikyou_smile]\AA[2]Kikyo: "You couldn't stay free anymore. It's a strange story
that you could understand each other because you became
monsters..."

\F[beni_nadeshy]\FF[syuu_laugh]\AA[2]Hiiragi: "But I never thought it would turn out this happy♪
It's nice, right? Pure love and all♪"

\F[beni_nadeshy]\FF[ayaka_laugh]\AA[2]Ayaka: "That's great! Knowing that you both have mutual
feelings is amazing! I wish you happiness... both of you!"

\F[beni_nadesmile]Akane: "What can I say... something like this... you must be
sick of it by now. When you think about it calmly..."

\F[beni_nadesmile]Akane: "Loving too much and becoming a monster like this...
it's enough to cool down a hundred-year love..."

\F[beni_nadesmile]\FF[nakosu_trouble]\AA[1]Akane: "But... there are no lies or secrets... My current
feelings are this form. I want to feel Nadeshiko with my
whole body..."

\F[beni_nadeshy]\FF[nakosu_smile]\AA[2]Nadeshiko: "I still have some aftereffects from when I
turned into a monster. My thoughts are a bit too free, or
rather, honest..."

\F[beni_nadeshy]\FF[nakosu_smile]\AA[2]Nadeshiko: "Don't ask twice. It's always... taking
forever..."

\F[beni_nadesmile]\FF[nakosu_shy]\AA[2]Nadeshiko: "Y-yeah, it's okay... Just for today, it's
special..."

\F[beni_nadesmile]\FF[nakosu_shy]\AA[1]Akane: "Yeah. I'll hold you for a lifetime. I won't let go
anymore."

\F[beni_nadesmile]\FF[nakosu_shy]\AA[2]Nadeshiko: "Continuing today for a lifetime... It's like
you're proposing..."
\F[beni_nadesmile]\FF[nakosu_shy]\AA[1]Akane: "If it was a proposal, would you accept it?"
